{"tid":672363,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Winning = 有線, FIFA = now？","createTime":"2018-05-21T02:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T02:46:54.000Z","uid":57405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4eaec97a940b2aa6c4e5a3d75d62c888c35361dd","tid":672363,"uid":57405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T02:45:34.000Z","msg":"Winning今個月同歐聯解左約，意味著《Winning Eleven 2019》將不會再有歐聯的正版授權。<br />\n巧合地，有線電視同歐聯既合約又係今年完，唔知會唔會一齊投向now tv同FIFA懷抱呢？<br />\n<br />\n香港收費電視界內，有線同now一直爭奪歐洲各頂級聯賽播映權；電競界就有Winning同FIFA爭各大聯賽正名授權。<br />\n<br />\n各自命運其實一樣，Winning同有線曾經有過輝煌歷史，即使冇英超，仍有西甲、歐聯，但已成過去；FIFA同now則不斷擴展，現時已把英超、西甲、德甲獨攬在手。"},{"pid":"ac7bac98860cc4086c1faddbbfa5649b5eb2d958","tid":672363,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T02:46:17.000Z","msg":"r/soccerstream"},{"pid":"dd969e1646684c4b8815b69276cecda50c0687bb","tid":672363,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T02:46:54.000Z","msg":"r/soccerstream<span style=\"color: red;\">s</span>"}]}